{"id": "1204517589196472340", "channel_id": "1204517589196472340", "type": 0, "author_id": "968857106985910302", "author_name": "enosred", "author_bot": false, "content": "如题。\n事先声明我并没有吃过一次死扛，但怪蛇残蜕并没有触发增加死亡抗性的效果，从视频里可以看到只触发了增加临时力量的效果。", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T20:02:52.119000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1204517589808844800", "filename": "RPReplay_Final1707249240.mov", "content_type": "video/quicktime", "size": 4248941, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1204517589196472340/1204517589808844800/RPReplay_Final1707249240.mov?ex=6a003bac&is=69feea2c&hm=f564eb146c7c96971ad0e9a52d91fd65b73cd13ee4f8f069619df387378418e2&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204517589196472340", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」怪蛇残蜕的增加死亡抗性没有触发", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1204413075525074984", "channel_id": "1204413075525074984", "type": 0, "author_id": "242675237311873034", "author_name": "yon08", "author_bot": false, "content": "活動開始後不久就修改了可以使用兩倍體力消耗這點很不錯，但消耗體力需要花費不少時間，對於空閒時間難把控的玩家來說還是很難解決問題。我建議改用「進入關卡不耗費體力，而是在完成關卡後給予一個活動期間的兌換道具，此道具能搭配體力扣除給予玩家活動代幣」\n這樣好處有兩點：\n\n1.玩家可以不耗體亦無獎勵的多次遊玩享受活動關卡的樂趣\n\n2.玩家可以在不方便遊玩但體力要溢出時直接用先前遊玩通關獲得的道具快速消耗體力\n\n（這樣應該不會影響玩家在線時長的kpi吧？😅）", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T13:07:34.118000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204413075525074984", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」關於這次活動體力使用上的優化", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1204446399148859432", "channel_id": "1204446399148859432", "type": 0, "author_id": "963817092677787688", "author_name": "falst_over_", "author_bot": false, "content": "未來會不會有針對節慶出的角色然後一年復刻一次之類的", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T15:19:59.089000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204446399148859432", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」限定角色", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1204362046854930453", "channel_id": "1204362046854930453", "type": 0, "author_id": "428434526327406602", "author_name": "ed2800", "author_bot": false, "content": "因為目前體力上限是180\n\n活動雙倍一次需要120\n補充劑一包也是120\n如果不想等時間吃回體是必定溢出\n對強迫症非常的不友好😂\n=>希望能推出60或更小面額的可存放製劑。\n\n另外領取每日補給的180點也\n都會溢出\n=>希望能改成60×3的可存放製劑。\n\n\n或是直接提高體力上限到240也可以解決以上問題😂", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T09:44:47.935000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 8}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204362046854930453", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」有關靈啡肽補充包的size", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
